**Author:** [[*user weiserthanyou]]
[[include :scp-wiki:info:end]]

[[=]]
//Welcome to my author page,//
//have a look around//
//anything I've posted here is waiting to be found.//
//I'll build a mountain of content,//
//some better, some worse.//
//If none of it's of interest to you, enjoy this little verse.//
[[/=]]


+ About Me
[[div class="darkbox"]]
Oh, yeah, forgot you lot were coming.

Hi! I'm [[*user weiserthanyou]][[span class="fnnum"]].[[/span]][[span class="fncon"]]DISCLAIMER: May or may not be wiser than you.[[/span]], and welcome to my --crib-- author page. Come on in! Let me show you 'round. It's a little desolate here at the moment, but that'll change soon enough. I've been reading SCPs since 2016, but it took until 2021 to publish the first article of my own. I've written a few more and don't plan to stop, though. I've also spread to the Wanderer's Library! 
[[/div]]
+ My Works
[[div class="darkbox"]]
+++ Mainlist Entries

++++ - [*http://www.scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-6374 SCP-6374] - Even A Dead God Can Dream

//The Dreamer had not stirred in aeons.//


++++ - [*http://www.scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-5458 SCP-5458] - 'Til Death Do Us Part

//I'll see you in Hell soon enough.//


++++ - [*http://www.scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-6581 SCP-6581] - The Sunken Grave

//A black-haired man in golden robes with a crown and a purple flame over his head, standing above a kneeling crowd.
//


++++ - [*http://www.scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-6364 SCP-6364] - ⬢Hexagons are the Bestagons!⬢  [[span class="fnnum"]].[[/span]][[span class="fncon"]]Rewritten from [[*user Dr Asteria]].[[/span]]
//I aspire to the purity of the blessed graphene.//


++++ - [*http://www.scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-7771 SCP-7771] - As Luck Would Have It [[span class="fnnum"]].[[/span]][[span class="fncon"]]Collab with [[*user Dr Asteria]].[[/span]]
//If we can’t control the number of times we roll the dice, then we have to get the odds on our side. The house always wins.//

